Experienced software engineer with 8+ years developing scalable web applications...

responsibilities: Developed full-stack web applications using React and Node.js
Managed PostgreSQL databases and wrote complex queries
Participated in agile sprint planning and daily standups
Integrated third-party APIs and payment systems
achievements: Built customer dashboard used by 50,000+ users
Led migration from monolith to microservices

projects: Open source contributor to React ecosystem
Built real-time chat application handling 100K concurrent users
Developed ML pipeline for recommendation system
publications: Technical blog on microservices best practices (2022)

structuredData.summary: Experienced software engineer with 8+ years developing scalable web applications and leading engineering teams. Proven track record of delivering high-quality solutions, optimizing system performance, and mentoring developers. Expertise in full-stack development, microservices architecture, and cloud technologies.
